<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>CrWell</title>
  <style>
    body, html {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      height: 100%;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    #crwell-iframe {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border: none;
    }
    .loading {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100vh;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <% if @crwell_token.present? %>
    <iframe 
      id="crwell-iframe" 
      src="https://app.crwell.pro/?token=<%= @crwell_token %>"
      allow="camera; microphone; fullscreen; display-capture"
    ></iframe>
  <% else %>
    <div class="loading">
      <div>
        <h2>Carregando CrWell...</h2>
        <p>Por favor, fa√ßa logout e login novamente no Chatwoot para ativar o SSO.</p>
        <p>Ou acesse diretamente: <a href="https://app.crwell.pro" target="_blank">app.crwell.pro</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  <% end %>
</body>
</html>
